extendedInfo.description: Truck Parking 3DTest your driving and parking skills in this new and exciting 3D Truck Parking game! A UNIQUE DRIVING EXPERIENCE WITH GORGEOUS 3D GRAPHICSYour goal in this game is to park in the designated locations while avoiding obstacles. There is a time limit to keep you on your toes. If you have never driven a truck or bus before, then this game will give you that unique experience of driving a large vehicle. It's very different experience from driving a sportscar or a compact car like you may have experienced in racing games such as "Need for Speed", "Asphalt 7", or "Gran Turismo". Your precision driving skills will be tested and pushed to the limit!Truck Parking 3D features:â 12 Exciting levels, with more levels coming soon!â Beautiful 3D graphicsâ Unique Truck driving experience, including a Truck trailer!â A pro version of the game with more levels is coming soon!Like our game? Check out our website more of our games. http://www.3dgameexperience.comKeywords: truck, parking, driving, 3d, simulator, simulationIn order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.This app sends occasional push notification advertisements to your notification bar. You can easily opt out of these at http://www.airpush.com/optout

reviews.title: Great game BUT!!!
reviews.comment: It needs to be able to save levels after you pass them. If you quit playing it always starts you back at the 6th level. Will stop playing it till that issue is fixed!
reviews.author: Shawn Shearer

reviews.title: Pretty neat
reviews.comment: Its pretty neat. Good graphics an good control, as well as the pretty close to reality factor. I drive semi\'s for a living so once I got use to the controls I blew through it
reviews.author: Chris Miller

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: This game is great... While playing this game u totaly get focus on it... N its also improve ur thinking capacity... ;-)
reviews.author: Vivek Nigade

reviews.title: Actually a great concept
reviews.comment: When I first started to get my cdl, I sat in a bar with a toy truck, trying to get the hang of how it moves. This is a great concept but if this is supposed to try and give people an idea of how the trailer follows the tractor it needs to be from a birds eye view.
reviews.author: James Ghormley

reviews.title: Major spam adds
reviews.comment: Misleading license agreement if u don\'t pay attention. Make sure you decline it. Either way will cause pop ups and fake adds. Game isn\'t horrible if you don\'t mind the spam
reviews.author: Joey Ciresi

reviews.title: Td
reviews.comment: Need to see better. I\'m a truck driver. You should be able to see out front. Good app though
reviews.author: brian papai

reviews.title: Good game but needs a fix!
reviews.comment: Everytime you quit it brings you back to level 6 no matter how far along you get. Good game but this ruins it for me for sure.
reviews.author: Justin Clements

reviews.title: Good game..
reviews.comment: But why it still unlock until level 6. I already play until level 10 and exit the game after that. When i open the game again, level 7 and after still lock. Pls fix it.
reviews.author: ambrose john

reviews.title: Needs work
reviews.comment: Great game, but it doesn\'t save ur progress!! Plus there needs to b an overhead camera view option. Just so annoying everytime I open it I have to play 3-4 levels I\'ve already played to get back to where I was. Otherwise it\'d be 5 stars.
reviews.author: Adam Mcneel

reviews.title: Air Push Sucks and Other Ideas
reviews.comment: If I make it to level 6 and quit, I have to start all over again... ?? Also, after level has been started it would be cool if the \"tip\" message disappeared while driving... App is really cool, I dig it! But uninstalled immediately after first notification for \"now hiring\" The air push ads SUCK... Nice app but ads wrecked it... LG Elite..
reviews.author: Mathew B.

reviews.title: More fun than you\'d think, but don\'t download it.
reviews.comment: I work with a lot of truckers, so this is pretty funny, to put yourself in their place...  However, this game is bogged down by ads and push software. Keep data collection and identity theft out of your system.
reviews.author: J. Michael Freelon

reviews.title: Fun game. Needs camera view options on version that allows more time.
reviews.comment: Gives the feel of driving a real truck. I\'m a recent grad of a truck driving school n this game brings back that joy n excitement. Love the game. Think it would be better if the side mirrors were available in the version that allows more time.
reviews.author: Bruce Jackson

reviews.title: Awful game
reviews.comment: I am a trucker this game is awful the mechanics are terrible, controls clumsy... Do not bother!!!!
reviews.author: Kevin Kerr

reviews.title: Fefe
reviews.comment: Great great and great ! This game really train you to drive with carefully and with tact a real truck. It is good to download it.
reviews.author: Jean Andre Ferjuste

reviews.title: Virus alert
reviews.comment: Do not install. Upon installation AVG informed me that it had virus intrusive adware. Uninstalled straight away
reviews.author: Richard Firth

reviews.title: Great but
reviews.comment: It needs work I keep geting spam and app shortcuts I dont want  Apart from that fantastatic but could do with some more levels. Will rate 5 stars if these issues are sorted
reviews.author: Adam Piper

reviews.title: Don\'t install
reviews.comment: The game itself is fun, but you get spam messages that constantly pop up on your phone. I didn\'t listen to the other reviews about that problem, but trust us its real. I uninstalled after the fourth or fifth spam message. Sad that they do this. I will never install one of their games again.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Its cool
reviews.comment: I like the game. My one large complaint is that it does not save your progress so you have to start over each time. Fix this and the lag on the steering wheel and it will get least a 4 maybe 5. Its a fun game and i do recommend it.
reviews.author: Jim Dailey

reviews.title: Cool
reviews.comment: I injoyed the first game soj I\'m now injoying my secound game with many other game from Google play, thank you ; Bobbiemcgee.  The viewer sucks
reviews.author: Justin Carlson

reviews.title: Great?!
reviews.comment: Depends on how you define great! The spam all day long sucks! And if you accidentally hit the notification you start getting calls for career advice. The game is awesome but I don\'t recommend it because of the spam!
reviews.author: Jennae Brookover
